# Dashboard

The dashboard provides an operational overview of your organization's compliance status.

Widgets include:

- Expiring Soon
- Expired
- Assigned to Me
- Pending Approval
- Recent Activity
- Compliance Score
- Notifications

Selecting any widget opens the associated filtered record list.

