# Frequently Asked Questions

How do I renew a certificate?

Open the record and select Renew.

Who can delete certificates?

Administrators only.

Can I recover deleted records?

If your retention policy permits.

Can I export reports?

Yes.

Can I upload multiple documents?

Yes.

Can I edit historical records?

Only with appropriate permissions.